@startuml User_Friends
title User Friends Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "User Controller" as Ctrl
database "Database" as DB
participant "Security Log" as Log

== Send Request ==
User -> FE: Send Friend Request
FE -> API: POST /users/friend/request
API -> Ctrl: Validate Target
Ctrl -> DB: Find User & Update Requests
Ctrl -> Log: Log Friend Request
Ctrl --> API: Success

== Respond to Request ==
User -> FE: Accept/Reject Request
FE -> API: POST /users/friend/respond
API -> Ctrl: Validate
Ctrl -> DB: Update Friend List
Ctrl -> Log: Log Response
Ctrl --> API: Success

@enduml
